item.title: About me
item.description: I am Wenping Zou, a Ph.D. majored in Chemistry. Prior to obtain my Ph.D. degree in University of Houston at 2022, I earned my bachelor degree of Polymer Engineering in HeFei University of Technology at 2014 and the master degree in Polymer Chemistry& Physics in University of Science and Technology of China at 2017. Now my research interests focus on studies of microbiology and fluorescent proteins You can view my CV here.
